Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:52.10,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,你們等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:16:01.15,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,你們怎麼搞的 閃一邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.15,0:16:02.07,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,走開啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:43.98,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:36.67,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛啊
